Explicit Wait:  will wait for a specific element and specific condition.
                elementToBeClickable()    (clickable olana kadar bekler)
                visibilityOfElement()     (spesific olarak bi elementin visible olana kadar beklemesi)

     Implicit Wait
        1)  Is creating one time wait for the driver and it will affect the driver until the driver.quit() or
            execution is done.
        2)  Handling "noSuchElementException". will force the selenium wait before arousing the warning.

     Explicit Wait
        1)  We'll create explicit wait for a specific element.When the element executed, it will not affect anymore
        2)  Handling the exception depends on how we created
